title: Final Fantasy XI w/Free to Play Guide
description:
The latest update from Nasomi Community FFXI Server, soon to become Nasomi Community Services!

With over 150 dedicated players, we're striving to create the community of FFXI circa 2006. Regular xp parties are the norm, you'll find yourself playing with others more than you play with yourself!

Our content is up through ToAU with a focus on CoP. You start with standard items and gil, and xp at normal rates. All rates are 100% retail for the 2006 era. Minor adjustments

The installation instructions are in the torrent that explains step by step how to become part of a great community, or you can visit our site and forums at http://www.nasomi.com/ if you run into trouble.

You can also use the install to play retail FFXI.

Hope to see you in game!
